to have feelings for him.

251
00:16:54,765 --> 00:16:56,433
No, I'm not.

252
00:16:56,558 --> 00:16:58,560
Feelings aren't rational.

253
00:16:58,686 --> 00:17:00,145
I know you have trouble
with anything

254
