276
00:18:09,715 --> 00:18:12,259
One-millimeter cut
through upper abdomen.

277
00:18:12,384 --> 00:18:15,137
She was adopted when the parents
thought they couldn't have kids.

278
00:18:15,262 --> 00:18:16,430
Then they had three more.

279
00:18:16,555 --> 00:18:18,640
