00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:50,798
You lost track of your speed?

291
00:18:51,673 --> 00:18:55,969
I think that was Hitler's excuse,
"Lost track of the Jews."

292
00:18:56,094 --> 00:18:57,554
No one held him responsible.

293
00:18:57,679 --> 00:18:58,931
I'm not playing, House.

294
00:18:59,056 --> 00:19:00,390
