312
00:19:44,935 --> 00:19:47,187
If Wilson was getting handcuffed
on the hood of his car,

313
00:19:47,312 --> 00:19:49,106
would I be carrying
on a differential?

314
00:19:49,231 --> 00:19:51,191
Diameter's at least
eight centimeters.

315
00:19:52,442 --> 00:19:53,944
Is it in the tail or the head?

316
00:19:54,069 --> 00:19:55,112
<i>The head.</i>

317
00:19:55,237 --> 00:19:57,406
You, too, sir, out of the car.

318
00:19:57,531 --> 00:19:59,908
We've got a construction site.

319
00:20:00,033 --> 00:20:02,119
A steamroller is plowing...

320
00:20:03,161 --> 00:20:04,413
Out, now.

321
00:20:08,876 --> 00:20:10,252
No cane.

322
00:20:21,179 --> 00:20:25,893
James Evan Wilson. There's a warrant
for your arrest in Louisiana.

323
00:20:34,902 --> 00:20:36,862
What are the traits
of a steamroller?

324
00:20:36,987 --> 00:20:39,281
Powerful.
Maybe pancreatic cancer.

325
00:20:39,406 --> 00:20:41,241
Great idea.
Except the only symptom

326
00:20:41,366 --> 00:20:44,036
it matches up with
is being steamroller-ish.

327
00:20:44,161 --> 00:20:45,722
You don't think House
is onto something?

328
00:20:45,829 --> 00:20:47,664
I think he thought
he had an idea.

329
00:20:47,789 --> 00:20:51,835
I also think his metaphors are tough
enough to decipher after he's said them.

330
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,480
We need to be focusing
on the medicine.

331
00:20:53,545 --> 00:20:54,630
No answer.

332
00:20:54,755 --> 00:20:57,257
There's not going to be an answer.
They've been arrested.

333
00:20:57,382 --> 00:20:58,342
He was joking.

334
00:20:58,467 --> 00:21:00,427
He reacted to
the size and location.

335
00:21:00,552 --> 00:21:03,180
That's what we should be focusing on,
not playing Madlibs

336
00:21:03,305 --> 00:21:06,683
