00:34:59,849 --> 00:35:02,435
Did you know I was
going to do that?

590
00:35:02,560 --> 00:35:04,320
Because I didn't know
I was going to do that.

591
00:35:04,353 --> 00:35:06,773
I know you have trouble
losing people.

592
00:35:07,523 --> 00:35:09,400
In New Orleans,
I saw you carrying

593
00:35:09,525 --> 00:35:11,986
this express package
around the conference,

594
00:35:12,779 --> 00:35:16,032
and you wouldn't let it go,
but you wouldn't open it,

595
00:35:16,157 --> 00:35:18,201
so I peeked at
the return address.

596
00:35:18,326 --> 00:35:20,077
Diamond, Fairbarren.

597
00:35:20,203 --> 00:35:21,496
Divorce attorneys.

598
00:35:22,163 --> 00:35:24,165
Your first wife had just served you
