628
00:36:44,495 --> 00:36:46,330
They don't look more tan
than anyone else.

629
00:36:46,455 --> 00:36:47,582
Discolored teeth?

630
00:36:47,707 --> 00:36:50,251
They're farmers. Their village
doesn't even have a dentist.

631
00:36:50,376 --> 00:36:52,461
Right. Thanks.

632
00:36:52,587 --> 00:36:56,048
But if it matters,
I'm not convinced they were her parents.

633
00:36:56,173 --> 00:36:57,008
Why not?

634
00:36:57,133 --> 00:36:58,843
<i>Because they said
they had no daughter.</i>

635
00:36:58,968 --> 00:37:02,346
The man was adamant, and the woman
