the One Child Policy in 1979.

652
00:37:47,642 --> 00:37:49,894
Say they didn't want a girl.

653
00:37:50,019 --> 00:37:51,479
They tried to kill her.

654
00:37:51,604 --> 00:37:52,844
But maybe the baby doesn't die,

655
00:37:52,897 --> 00:37:55,024
