and the hair hides the entry wounds.

687
00:39:24,530 --> 00:39:25,865
It's the perfect crime.

688
00:39:25,990 --> 00:39:27,470
She's had them in her
all these years.

689
00:39:27,533 --> 00:39:28,617
What changed at the temple?

690
00:39:28,743 --> 00:39:30,703
Same thing that changed
in the MRI.

691
00:39:30,828 --> 00:39:33,372
<i>Shockingly,
not all religious leaders are honest.</i>

692
00:39:33,497 --> 00:39:35,857
<i>I'm guessing these particular monks
